SAWEETIE – TWO NEW TRACKS

Grammy®-nominated artist Saweetie releases two new singles that are sure to make waves in music and pop culture. She joins forces with fellow rap luminaries YG and Tyga for the club-ready new single “Birthday” and turns all the way up on “Shot O’ Clock.”

STR8 TO THE KLUB TOUR

The trio, Tyga, YG and Saweetie, will play 14 arena shows in 13 North American cities starting September 21 at Golden 1 Center in Sacramento and finishing at the KIA Forum in Los Angeles on November 22. The “STR8 TO THE KLUB TOUR” will include stops at the Chase Center in San Francisco, Thomas & Mack Center in Las Vegas, Tucson Arena in Tucson, PNE Forum in Vancouver, and Pechanga Arena.

SAWEETIE + TYGA + YG

Today, global icons YG, Tyga, and Saweetie have announced their upcoming Fall 2023 “STR8 TO THE KLUB TOUR.”
